40:33.431 --> 40:43.741 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
JUDY WOODRUFF: Yesterday,
special correspondent
Fred de Sam Lazaro brought us a
report on

40:43.775 --> 40:49.347 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
how big city street vendors are
being left
behind in India's booming
economy.

40:49.380 --> 40:54.285 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
Today, we travel to stone
quarries in the
rural northern part of the
country, where

40:54.319 --> 40:59.123 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
a deadly disease has trapped
workers there
in poverty for generations.

40:59.157 --> 41:02.226 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
This report is part of our
Agents for Change
series.

41:02.260 --> 41:09.600 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
FRED DE SAM LAZARO: Across the
urban landscape
rise majestic sandstone palaces,
monuments

41:09.634 --> 41:17.175 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
and temples, built in India's
timeless architectural
traditions.

41:17.208 --> 41:21.713 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
But what's also timeless is how
the stone
continues to be mined, far from
the cities

41:21.746 --> 41:27.285 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
here in the Rajasthan Desert.
Early each morning,
you hear the sound of sandstone
being pounded

41:27.318 --> 41:33.624 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
into a gravel that is used in
construction.
No one is spared the drudgery,
it seems, nursing

41:33.658 --> 41:37.095 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
mother with infant, young
children.

41:37.128 --> 41:39.564 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
QUESTION: How old are you?

41:39.597 --> 41:41.299 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
CHILD (through translator): Ten.

41:41.332 --> 41:44.902 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
FRED DE SAM LAZARO: He should be
in school.
It's the law. But history
suggests he will

41:44.936 --> 41:53.978 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
soon graduate to a quarry, part
of a vicious
cycle of generational poverty
and disease.

41:54.011 --> 42:01.953 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
The work is physically brutal
under a blazing
desert sun. Power drills are a
recent addition

42:01.986 --> 42:07.258 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
that have made these quarries
more productive.
But behind their thick clouds of
dust, miners

42:07.291 --> 42:12.930 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
wear nothing but flip-flops on
their feet-and
nothing at all on their faces.
They earn $2

42:12.964 --> 42:15.733 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
to $4 a day, depending on the
task.

42:15.767 --> 42:20.638 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
DR. PRAKASH TYAGI, Executive
Director, GRAVIS:
The law of the mines is that, no
work, no

42:20.671 --> 42:25.743 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
wage. So, the days when they
can't turn to
work, because of an illness or
because of

42:25.777 --> 42:27.979 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
some other problem, they can't
make any money.

42:28.012 --> 42:32.750 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
FRED DE SAM LAZARO: And, Prakash
Tyagi says,
for an alarming number, perhaps
a third of

42:32.784 --> 42:40.858 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
the 250,000 sandstone miners,
the work is
lethal, linked to silicosis, a
slow, irreversible

42:40.892 --> 42:42.960 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
loss of lung function.

42:42.994 --> 42:48.433 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
DR. PRAKASH TYAGI: Silicosis is
a shame. Silicosis
is something that shouldn't
exist in the contemporary

42:48.466 --> 42:50.334 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
times.

42:50.368 --> 42:53.738 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
FRED DE SAM LAZARO: Silicosis is
easily preventable
with face masks and by using
water to tamp

42:53.771 --> 42:59.410 align:left position:12.5%,start line:73.33% size:87.5%
down the dust that is
everywhere. And the
disease is now rarely seen in
developed countries.

42:59.444 --> 43:04.048 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
And yet Tyagi, who is a medical
doctor, says
no one around here had ever
addressed until

43:04.081 --> 43:09.420 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
about three decades ago, when
his late father
started a charity called GRAVIS,
dedicated

43:09.454 --> 43:13.191 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
to improving life in this
impoverished region.

43:13.224 --> 43:19.897 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
In the early days, many patients
they saw
were assumed to have
tuberculosis, which is

43:19.931 --> 43:21.666 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
treatable with antibiotics.

43:21.699 --> 43:25.803 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
DR. PRAKASH TYAGI: The treatment
was given.
Still, people were dying with
lung issues

43:25.837 --> 43:29.073 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
very similar to T.B. But it
wasn't T.B.

43:29.106 --> 43:34.445 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
FRED DE SAM LAZARO: Only after
sending 250
X-rays to a research center in
Delhi did GRAVIS

43:34.479 --> 43:40.718 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
learn it was dealing with
silicosis and designed
ways to help patient cope with
the slow, degenerative,

43:40.751 --> 43:43.020 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
fatal condition.

43:43.054 --> 43:49.393 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
Today, GRAVIS runs field clinics
near quarries,
offering diagnostic services and
a limited

43:49.427 --> 43:54.599 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
amount of drugs, like cough
suppressants and
inhalers that can control,
though not cure,

43:54.632 --> 43:55.833 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
symptoms.

43:55.867 --> 43:57.702 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
DR. PRAKASH TYAGI (through
translator): Do
you have T.B.?

43:57.735 --> 44:02.773 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
FRED DE SAM LAZARO: Many, like
this 25-year-old
mother of two, hope that they
just have T.B.,

44:02.807 --> 44:04.575 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
which is a common coinfection.

44:04.609 --> 44:10.181 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
However, the paper she carried,
but was unable
to read, indicated she had
silicosis.

44:10.214 --> 44:12.717 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
