44:12.750 --> 44:17.889 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
DR. PRAKASH TYAGI: At the most.
So, she's
one of those accelerated
silicosis cases.

44:17.922 --> 44:22.493 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
