16.

44:24.462 --> 44:29.267 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
FRED DE SAM LAZARO: Many start
even younger,
though it typically takes about
20 years of

44:29.300 --> 44:35.806 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
dust exposure for silicosis to
develop, destroying
lung tissue, rendering sufferers
listless

44:35.840 --> 44:37.875 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
and unable to do much physical
activity.

44:37.909 --> 44:43.581 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
MAN (through translator): I have
been ill
for about seven years. For two
years I have

44:43.614 --> 44:45.449 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
