at all.

44:45.483 --> 44:50.087 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
FRED DE SAM LAZARO: Their
condition will worsen
inevitably, until, like Joga Ram
(ph), they

44:50.121 --> 44:52.390 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
