44:52.423 --> 44:57.628 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
DR. PRAKASH TYAGI: This is how,
typically,
silicosis patients die.

44:57.662 --> 45:00.698 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
FRED DE SAM LAZARO: Is he
reasonably comfortable
or is he in pain?

45:00.731 --> 45:02.433 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
DR. PRAKASH TYAGI: He's in a lot
of pain.

45:02.466 --> 45:07.438 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
FRED DE SAM LAZARO: Ideally, he
would receive
oxygen and steroids and die in a
hospital

45:07.471 --> 45:12.410 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
