is available
or affordable here.

45:12.443 --> 45:18.549 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
The prolonged illness forces
many families
to incur debt, prolonging their
medieval poverty

45:18.583 --> 45:20.284 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
into the next generation.

45:20.318 --> 45:26.390 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
Modu Devi (ph) echoed the
sentiments of many
in this group of silicosis
widows.

45:26.424 --> 45:31.162 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
WOMAN (through translator): We
have to send
our children to work. We have no
choice. There

45:31.195 --> 45:33.731 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
