our stomachs.

45:33.764 --> 45:39.170 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
FRED DE SAM LAZARO: It's not a
lot of food.
It was around 10:00 a.m. when we
visited this

45:39.203 --> 45:40.137 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
