45:53.985 --> 45:56.020 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
QUESTION (through translator):
How much will
you get paid?

45:56.053 --> 45:57.788 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
WOMAN (through translator): One
hundred and
fifty.

45:57.822 --> 46:03.127 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
FRED DE SAM LAZARO: That's about
