46:03.160 --> 46:08.366 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
These magnificent sandstone from
which government
officials governs in New Delhi
may seem aloof

46:08.399 --> 46:14.138 align:left position:12.5%,start line:73.33% size:87.5%
