indifference and
poor education ensure laws are
rarely enforced.

46:30.154 --> 46:33.924 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
This mine owner insisted that he
makes masks
and helmets available.

46:33.958 --> 46:38.429 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
