the next mine,"
he said.

46:44.635 --> 46:49.140 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
For their part, workers said
they sometimes
used masks while drilling, but
in the blazing

46:49.173 --> 46:52.209 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
