48:59.937 --> 49:01.739 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
Day.

49:01.772 --> 49:03.574 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
PADMA LAKSHMI, Author, "Love,
Loss, and What
We Ate": Somebody approached me
at a bar one

49:03.607 --> 49:08.412 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
night who was a friend of a
friend and thought
I could model. And, at the time,
