I am not going to ruin my GPA in
the last

49:13.684 --> 49:20.090 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
semester.

49:20.124 --> 49:25.729 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
I have a very complicated and
layered relationship
with modeling. It has allowed me
to travel,

49:25.763 --> 49:30.835 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
