as a nurse
to make in a month.

49:35.573 --> 49:40.444 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
I know that my looks are really
the alchemy
of my parents' genetics and have
little to

49:40.477 --> 49:44.548 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
do with me or any accomplishment
of my own.

49:44.582 --> 49:50.020 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
Food and fashion are both much
closer than
people realize. You can tell a
lot about a

49:50.054 --> 49:55.793 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
