have great
metabolisms. And that is the
truth.

50:05.636 --> 50:12.109 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
One of the biggest fringe
benefits of having
a measure of success and being
in the public

50:12.142 --> 50:17.448 align:left position:12.5%,start line:80% size:87.5%
eye is being able to do
something good for
other people.

50:17.481 --> 50:23.354 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
I think the proudest moment for
my family,
