chronic pain.

50:47.878 --> 50:54.018 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
It's something that I have
suffered from all
my life, and it was a silent and
deadly shadow.

50:54.051 --> 50:58.989 align:left position:12.5%,start line:73.33% size:87.5%
There's no cure for
endometriosis, but there
is certainly very good treatment
out there.

50:59.023 --> 51:04.862 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
And if you find it early in a
young girl's
life, you can change her life
forever.

51:04.895 --> 51:13.771 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
